# ── Default-deny whitelist — hanya artefak publik yang ter-track ──
# Filosofi: tolak SEMUA dulu, izinkan eksplisit. File instruktur/rahasia
# (soal, rubrik, demo-script, runbook, rehearsal) tak pernah masuk git.
# GitHub Pages meng-serve repo ini di <user>.github.io/<repo>/

# sampah — selalu tolak
**/.DS_Store

# tolak semua di root repo
/*

# izinkan tooling + landing
!.gitignore
!.nojekyll
!index.html

# ── roe: deck Rule of Engagement (pra-sesi, publik) ──
!roe/
roe/*
!roe/slides/
roe/slides/*
!roe/slides/index.html
!roe/slides/img/

# ── deck slide per minggu: w01 + w02 publik ──
# (w03–w07 sengaja TIDAK di-whitelist → LOCAL. w04 battle soal aman.)
# w03/w05 masih di-limit dari publik (2026-07-15) — kartunya di index.html = "Segera".
!w01/
!w02/
w0*/*
!w01/slides/
!w02/slides/

# ── w01: dokumen peserta (exercise + handout + definisi proyek) ──
!w01/exercise.md
!w01/handout.md
!w01/assets/
w01/assets/*
!w01/assets/project-definition.json

# ── w02: dokumen peserta (exercise + handout + panduan + troubleshooting + setup-check) ──
!w02/exercise.md
!w02/handout.md
!w02/panduan-peserta.md
!w02/troubleshooting.md
!w02/assets/
w02/assets/*
!w02/assets/setup-check.sh
# runbook.md (materi fasilitator) + slides-outline.md (draft superseded) → LOCAL

# ── _shared: hanya dokumen peserta (bukan doc build-internal) ──
!_shared/
_shared/*
!_shared/persiapan-peserta.md
!_shared/versions.md
!_shared/CLAUDE.md
# stage-setup.md + bootstrap-stage.sh → LOCAL (materi pemateri, TAK di-publish)
!_shared/templates/
# seed/ (dipakai grademe, bukan materi sesi) · build-week-handson.md · deck-engine.md → LOCAL (tak di-whitelist)
